Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Spare me...{unsure what he means, mou iya is "already no/bad"}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,An artificial ski resort, then? \NWe can start special training now.{/I'm trusting you to conduct a special training for me}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I make Honmaru small.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Trunsform!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.23,0:04:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't forget I'm fragile!{/I trust you to be gentle; lit: please be soft with your hands}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.91,0:04:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.{/Leave this to me/trust me}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We get to the mountain top first.{/climbing up the mt}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, can start skiing from here.{/you slide/ski from here}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,From the very top already?{I think he means "my first ride is already from the very top?"}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, Limpy-kun will aid special training.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru Jump!{unsure, maybe it's a trick name since he used the english word, maybe a command}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{high?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru Grande Spin!{unsure if maybe there are special terms for that in skiing; it's "san kaiten" in manga but I hear "dai kaiten" here}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, doing great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to ski well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Laden with bentos, our stooped backs,{おべんといっぱい背にしょって - full of lunch boxes on our back}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.75,0:05:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Out we go, merrily, to have a picnic{(行くぞたのしいピクニック)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.84,0:05:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Road of 500 miles begins with a step{千里の道も一歩から}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we keep walking, we'll get anywhere{/if I walk, I'll get anywhere in no time - (歩くよ真っ直ぐどこまでも)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:06:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We're barely out of the tunnel, \Nbut in the Land of Snow already!{only half-sure about "nuketara" - "to emerge from" the rest is a mystery; last word sounds a lot like 雪国 - "snow country; snowy region​"; first word should be something along the lines of "tunnel" even if I cant determine the exact word for sure; TLC?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can even see the ski resort from here!{has to be スキー場}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite a sight, isn't it?{only hear sugee}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, everyone, we're almost at the ski resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you don't forget your things.{lit is "finish/complete/put away your between-meal snack​/afternoon refreshment" - no clue what's this about, we don't see anyone eating anything and they are still far enough to gobble a bun should you want to, so even if it hurts me, I have to discard the original line here, we in the west have no notion of such things so I deem it better this way}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The scenery is heaven-like here, Iyona-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Skiing is so much against my nature!{/I hate skiing so much!}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Even dying in a car crash \Nseems actually preferable to this!{/if only we'd get in an accident and the whole thing is cancelled...}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Me bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd you manage to get hurt here?{/what could this scar be}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts! I swear, gimme a break at least here...{/it doesn't matter at all/not your concern}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this brings back memories. \NThe pristine-white snow of Alps...{/yes, I remember; アスピリンスノー / aspirin snow seems to be just a sort of snowflakes}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Honmaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm cool, cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The vast silver-white slopes{it's the same word as in episoded title but other reading} of Matterhorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, Iyona-san! \NNext time, we should go toge—{/when we arrive, together with me...}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We would go ski together, right, Honmaru-kun?{/lets slide together, okay?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised to teach me plenty.{/teach me various things, okay?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can leave that to me! \NI was dubbed Edojo Skimaru{-sama - usually I'd include but this is already cps-heavy and sama here is not very conspicuous} for a reason!{/you should trust me this, this great edojo skimaru-sama}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.50,0:07:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I'm relying heavily on magic today...{/in that case I've no choice but magic}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.87,0:07:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Please cover me, Taru!{/I'm begging you/counting on}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Huh? Not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... Hey! Hey, where's Taruruuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But what's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? Driver?!{actually ittai - strong word for "what in the world" but it doesn't sound all that well in en}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.74,0:07:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Here! No worries, I'm covering for driver.{/I sorry, I gave you chauffeur replacement}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This very fun!{/interesting}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.38,0:07:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you even get here?!{/why, you...}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't allow this!{/stop it - changin to make it sound as though she want to steer too}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Teacher wants to drive, too?{unsure if this is what he means, lit is "sensei also does?"}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.93,0:07:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowly bring it to a stop, Taru-kun.{not sure what is chotto, maybe "quickly" maybe "for a second [give me the wheel]"}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, be reasonable. {absolute guess, kinda wanna hear "mite" there; TLC?} {7:53: I'm hearing 先生めちゃくちゃ https://jisho.org/word/%E7%9B%AE%E8%8C%B6%E8%8B%A6%E8%8C%B6\NEssentially lit. "professor, (you're being) unreasonable"\NCould also use, "reckless" just to make the scene a bit more absurd.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:11.36,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(900,0)\c&H122126&\3c&H429FB4&\blur1}Dangerous\NCurve{カーブ キケン}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll crash now... {absolute guess as well Ochitsukare? Otsukare? TLC?} {I'm hearing ぶ、ぶつかれ\Nlit. to collide with / to hit etc...\NSomething like "We're going to crash" could work here.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,OH MY GOD! {won't even try to guess, daichotto? TLC? not really counting on you to fix any of those unhearable ones, but maybe you come up with a bright substitute, btw} {Haruko is literally screaming OH MY GOD!\NIt's just really drawn out. - Au}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why me?!{guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.35,0:08:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, oh no! \NI can't die while I'm still so young!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But I haven't even finished my lunch...{maybe this is what mari's earlier line was referring to, but it's still too distant / vague a callback to relate to}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the way, you all have to save me!{really unsure what he means, assuming he wants everyone to be under him to make for a cushion when hitting the ground; lit though is "I will save you" so maybe he intends to save them somehow by beating them up? idk}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the only heir to the Harako Conglomerate!{/scion of harako zaibatsu}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, everyone! \NCalm down now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.27,0:08:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who needs to calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! This is not the time for fighting!{/quarrels/arguing}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Get along while you can!{/let's get along}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll really end up dying in a car crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:09:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case... \NIn that case, Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy at last...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Taruru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:18.50,Sign,,0,0,0,,{Heisei tourism/sightseeing - 平成観光 - this does not seem to be a joke of any sort so I'm not including this}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A clean landing, like in the good old days!{/I'm the best!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think? \NI used to be pretty good at skiing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think? \NI cast a Time-Freezing Spell to bring bus to life!{very unsure, he just says "I cast a time-stopping magic" no clue what is this douda or who is he asking this question, would assume he had to stop the time to draw a face on the bus, hence we never saw him doing that, they cut this part from manga and now it feels so haphazard - in manga he says "douda, honmaru?" but still no clarification of what he used the time-freeze for}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.88,0:09:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh! A bus!{guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.14,0:09:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Make way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is now \Nthe ski bus lane!{/the ski bus is coming through}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So many snacks yet to try!{lit: something is blowing - no clue what he means and also unsure it's fuite, maybe it's "somehow windy down here" or "something's pressing me down" or idk; TLC?} {There are two possible options for this line.\NThe first, なんか悔いて, in which 悔いて = to regret. (I'm guessing he regrets not doing something something.)\NThe second, なんか食ういて in which 食ういて = to eat. (I'm guessing he want to eat something, anything before he "dies")\NI'm inclined to think it's the second one since I've TL'd a similar line in another anime I worked on.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me run the hell away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.81,0:10:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.19,0:10:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan's scent...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,200)}Making a shortcut straight to the hotel!{/this way, going directly for the inn}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Any idea how in the hell we ended up here?{/just what the heck was it}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me...{/I wonder}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You did your best to protect me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.97,0:10:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,150)}Well, that was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:11:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My safety should be your concern, \Neven over your own safety!{unsure what he means by うまく助かったからいーようなものの - most likely "the fact I'm saved successfully is the best thing ever/You must be endlessly grateful I was saved"}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down! Calm down! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're the one who's least calm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?{/are you saying} I {\i1}am{\i0} calm!{guess, TLC} {11:05: I'm hearing 何言ってるの？普通のよ！https://jisho.org/word/%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A\NFor the second part it should be someting like "I am calm!"\NAll together it would be "What do you mean? I am calm!" - au}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.88,0:11:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,00)}And the weather is fine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(00,0)}Just what we need for an ideal day of skiing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Taruruuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you! Exhaust your magic, \Nbut make a convincing Edojo Skimaru out of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I can do it!{/trust me to do it}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Skimaru-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.33,0:11:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking forward to your teaching today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! I'll make sure not to disappoint you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.88,0:12:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.84,0:12:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A snow! Snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru Skimaru-sama is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.73,0:12:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What sort of skiing do you specialize in?{lit: what kind of sliding do you do}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.44,0:12:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They say Honmaru-kun was the interschool champion\Nwhen he was still in kindergarten!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.69,0:12:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad! The rumors are exaggerating it \Nto impossible levels!{/are spreading and becoming great/unrealistic}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive, Honmaru! \NYou keep rising in my eyes!{I hope this is what he means by "review; reconsideration; revision"}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, while we ski together, \Nlet me catch up with you once in a while, will you?{very unsure, methinks she means "while sliding at full speed/to full extent, you shouldn't leave me behind" but I suspect I'm wrong, lit is "while sliding rapidly/increasingly/more and more, ..." as though she means to say "while we ride, don't stray further and further away from me" TLC?} {You suspect right, actually. \NI'm interpreting this as something like "Don't go skiing off ahead and leave me/us behind, okay?"\NSince they all think he's some great skiier I think this line fits the context.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So cool...{/handsome}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Just trust me with this, people!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to witness this technique{/skiing} \Nof Edojo Skimaru-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been secretly developing it since I was three, \Nand today I'm letting you take a sneak peek at...{/Honmaru-sama who had started skiing at the age of three has been developing/advancing/improving in a blink of an eye/swiftly/before you notice}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sneak Peek~{\i0}{trying to reflect how this is not what he actually says but an afterthought, a realization of what he just said}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru! Aren't those your H-Filtering ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad{/oops}! I mistook Honmaru's goggles for my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not complaining.{/that's fine too}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, the beginners are handled \Nby Waseda-sensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,amateurs{/intermediate learners} - by Yamagata-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.28,0:13:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I myself will look after the advanced skiers.{/give guidance/teach/mentor}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear advanced skiers, \Nwe ain't slacking off here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done...{/this is bad}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, beginners gather right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.93,0:13:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you up to?{/doing}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, aren't you an advanced skier?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, I can't wait!{/let's go faster}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I just remembered, no matter how advanced you are, \Nyou should first do a basic warm-up!{/however good you are, first - solidify the basics}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the time to crack jokes.{unsure what is ギャグ here, would assume "don't talk baloney/become a braggard/joker"}
