Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.54,0:14:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let me down, Taruruuto...
Comment: 0,0:14:01.21,0:14:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Pero...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, more enthusiasm in the hips!{/put more effort/strength in your butt/thighs}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?! Taruruuto! \NWhy are you there?!{/what are you doing}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Honmaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's not how it's supposed to be! Hey!{/Why are you there}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru! I'm a reckless adventurer!{bouken is just "adventure; venture" but I think taru is excited and this is new to him so I'm making it sound as though he is doing something groundbreaking and important}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.10,0:14:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and join us here, Taru!{/come here sooner}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru! Skiing is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Taruruuto...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.41,0:14:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.98,0:14:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Taruruuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, what is this shiver I'm seeing?{/are you trembling}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?{/don't say nonsense} \NI'm just that excited, head to toe!{mushaburui is trembling with excitement}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Not everyone would dare throwing \Nan accusation that ridiculous at Skimaru-sama!{/this ... doesn't hear often anyone giving him such a mouth/such things said to him}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.72,0:14:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hope I muster enough guts \Nfor something worthy.{/in a case like this, the plan/strategy is figuring out something with guts/willpower}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is still more or less doable...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There are but the four of you \Nbrave enough to stay.{/the remaining people is just 4}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All are from my class. \NI knew you'd have the courage for this.{/you'll be alright if you're brave}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.79,0:15:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so royally screwed...{/truly in trouble}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's start with a lightning-fast slide \Nall the way to the ground.{most likely ikkini here is "in one breath/without stopping till the end"}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I will provide the rearguard myself, but we also need \Nsomeone with the top abilities to lead the vanguard.{/while the sensei will serve as a group's shingari, person in the head is the one more deft; Shingari is rear; rear unit guard/anchor (man); toppu here is 先頭 - vanguard}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! That would be Honmaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually like going after!{/I'm fine with after/later too}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I go after, that clear to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.69,0:15:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you getting so worked up about this?{/nothing to be so angry about}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.57,0:15:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Once everyone is away, \NI'll come clean before teacher.{/explain reasons/talk to ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then just take a lift down.{/descend via lift}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:15:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,First - Harako-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:15:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Second - Kawai-san!{hope its san}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What a sight!{/good}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Both are moving like pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad...{/impressive}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to witness the true extent \Nof Skimaru's talent!{/power/abilities}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,200)}But I don't {actually }know a thing about skiing!{/in reality I'm a noob at ski/can't ski}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.99,0:16:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This didn't come as a surprise to nobody.{/This, i had already understood}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing, Honmaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Was this Edojo Skimaru hoax \Na real thing all along?{/... wasn't a bluff}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.36,0:17:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually cool! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.24,0:17:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Not every gold medalist can be that good!{/he's like a ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.65,0:17:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do that...{/this is}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Heck yeah, that was my feat!{/thanks to me - it's important that he says "me" not "we" here}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll say your thanks later!{/you should be grateful}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! Taruruuto cast a spell for me in advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,People! Don't miss your chance to see \NEdojo Skimaru's dazzling skiing!{/have you seen the splendid ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A cloud descended on the slope?{no clue what's haku, but kumo must be some cloud; /inside a haku-cloud?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.69,0:17:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It was me who brought us thus far.{/thanks to me}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.48,0:17:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Heck no, it was me!{/wrong, thanks to me}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.25,0:17:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this about, you cheap braggart?{/would you look at this big-mouthed bastard/non-stop-talking}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell? Wanna go, you punk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How can one be so thick-headed?{cmplt guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the wreck that always goes sideways!{still a complete guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be fighting now!{/stop arguing}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard! You can't even ski by yourself! \N Don't you butt in when men quarrel!{really unsure what is すべれねくせに - lit is "despite sliding/when skiing, don't butt in/chime in with your mouth" - I sense a pun, but I can't figure it out, TLC?} {18:05: I'm hearing てめえ、滑るねくせに口を挟んじゃねぇ https://jisho.org/word/%E5%8F%A3%E3%82%92%E6%8C%9F%E3%82%80\NIn this context, 滑る means to ski.\NSo lit. You bastard! You can't even ski! Don't cut into our conversation!}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Working in tandem with you is unbearable!{/I can't do this together with you}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.79,0:18:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who's supposed to be saying that!{/this is my line}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll better off by myself!{/then look, I'm going this way}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Smell ya later!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Disunited again?!{mata ga sakeru - unsure what he means}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.34,0:18:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Incorpore-re-real!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Make way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Found you!{/I came}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There, his true colors finally show through!{/the mask fell off/sheep's clothing peeled off?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.31,0:19:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how to cast it right this time!{/use magic properly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Taruru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They're heading straight for the pit!{tanizoko is "valley floor; bottom of a gorge; bottom of a ravine"}
