Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.34,0:19:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No more infighting this way.{/this time we won't fight}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.49,0:19:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Single piece - single mind.{/one person for two pieces}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!{/is that so?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You see!{/that so - not sure what's the joke here}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say, Harako? \NThink you can still keep up with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing, Honmaru-kun!{hope its suteki}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare to defy{/challenge} me, \Nthe Junior Champion of the World?!{hope its zensekai}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The other side is unfit for skiing!{/there are no gerende on the other side - "ski slope(​From German “Gelände”)"}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.17,0:20:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This challenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.14,0:20:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,is not something I would decline!{/this challenge, I accept it}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, not backing down!{absolute guess, kochikochi?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never lose, Honmaru!{hope first word is ore}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.87,0:20:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Such an uncontrolled reaction \Nwon't do you any good, Harako!{muki ni naru is "to become too greedy/to fly off the handle over trivial things"}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.00,0:20:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No! With the prestige of the Harako family at stake, \Nlosing is not an option!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.50,0:20:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever thicket you're leading me through!{/inside any kind of woods}
