Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.41,0:22:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.57,0:22:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna play some cards with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.09,0:22:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Cards! Cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.16,0:22:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like I forgot to tend to something...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it'll be fine.{/well, whatever}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
