Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.58,0:22:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.44,0:22:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Taruru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.96,0:22:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.90,0:22:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, it's cold! \NNobody would be okay like this!
